<bug>
    <id>2804</id>
    <title>Accessing apps through the search box redirects user to  www.new.facebook.com/...  instead of  www.apps.facebook.com/... </title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Accessing apps through the Facebook s search box (on top of the page)_ I get redirected to:  www.new.facebook.com/...  instead of  apps.new.facebook.com/...</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Steps to reproduce:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">1 Visit the homepage.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.2">2 Type  (fluff  and use the down arrow key to select  (fluff)Friends  from suggestion list.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.3">3 Click enter.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Expect:
Browser redirect to  http://apps.new.facebook.com/fluff/main.php?ref=ts</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">Actual:
Browser redirect to  http://www.new.facebook.com/fluff/main.php?ref=ts</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="6">
            <sentence id="6.1">Currently using Windows 2003 and Firefox 2.0.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
